<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>last year, masp's new annex opened to the public.</title><link>https://rodigu.github.io/galleries/visita-anexo-masp/rss.xml</link><description></description><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 14 Feb 2026 13:58:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>https://getnikola.com/</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>it does not draw much attention to itself.</title><link>https://rodigu.github.io/galleries/visita-anexo-masp/masp-e-anexo.jpg</link><enclosure url="https://rodigu.github.io/galleries/visita-anexo-masp/masp-e-anexo.jpg" length="301483" type="image/jpeg"></enclosure><guid isPermaLink="false">galleries/visita-anexo-masp/masp-e-anexo.jpg</guid><pubDate>Sat, 29 Mar 2025 11:12:57 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>while contrasting the original building by bobardi.</title><link>https://rodigu.github.io/galleries/visita-anexo-masp/masp-e-anexo-lado.jpg</link><enclosure url="https://rodigu.github.io/galleries/visita-anexo-masp/masp-e-anexo-lado.jpg" length="159792" type="image/jpeg"></enclosure><guid isPermaLink="false">galleries/visita-anexo-masp/masp-e-anexo-lado.jpg</guid><pubDate>Sat, 29 Mar 2025 11:13:11 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>the annex is out of place and discrete at the same time.</title><link>https://rodigu.github.io/galleries/visita-anexo-masp/anexo-visao.jpg</link><enclosure url="https://rodigu.github.io/galleries/visita-anexo-masp/anexo-visao.jpg" length="326318" type="image/jpeg"></enclosure><guid isPermaLink="false">galleries/visita-anexo-masp/anexo-visao.jpg</guid><pubDate>Sat, 29 Mar 2025 11:13:43 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>the annex was actually built on top of a pre-existing building. they reused some of the foundations and original structure.</title><link>https://rodigu.github.io/galleries/visita-anexo-masp/moca-masp-escuro.jpg</link><enclosure url="https://rodigu.github.io/galleries/visita-anexo-masp/moca-masp-escuro.jpg" length="72044" type="image/jpeg"></enclosure><guid isPermaLink="false">galleries/visita-anexo-masp/moca-masp-escuro.jpg</guid><pubDate>Sat, 29 Mar 2025 16:17:43 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>using the tiny camera is lots of fun. i get to print and see the image as soon as they are taken. the paper is also cheap. i could even reuse regular print paper, which is something i do actually want to try out in the future.</title><link>https://rodigu.github.io/galleries/visita-anexo-masp/anexo-masp.jpg</link><enclosure url="https://rodigu.github.io/galleries/visita-anexo-masp/anexo-masp.jpg" length="251213" type="image/jpeg"></enclosure><guid isPermaLink="false">galleries/visita-anexo-masp/anexo-masp.jpg</guid><pubDate>Thu, 26 Jun 2025 10:16:06 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>a few weeks before that, i bought a tiny thermal camera that prints on receipt paper.</title><link>https://rodigu.github.io/galleries/visita-anexo-masp/cadeirinhas.jpg</link><enclosure url="https://rodigu.github.io/galleries/visita-anexo-masp/cadeirinhas.jpg" length="168845" type="image/jpeg"></enclosure><guid isPermaLink="false">galleries/visita-anexo-masp/cadeirinhas.jpg</guid><pubDate>Thu, 26 Jun 2025 10:17:02 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>i had the opportunity to visit at opening week.</title><link>https://rodigu.github.io/galleries/visita-anexo-masp/janelas-paulista.jpg</link><enclosure url="https://rodigu.github.io/galleries/visita-anexo-masp/janelas-paulista.jpg" length="216954" type="image/jpeg"></enclosure><guid isPermaLink="false">galleries/visita-anexo-masp/janelas-paulista.jpg</guid><pubDate>Thu, 26 Jun 2025 10:17:12 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>last year, masp's new annex opened to the public.</title><link>https://rodigu.github.io/galleries/visita-anexo-masp/poste-fio.jpg</link><enclosure url="https://rodigu.github.io/galleries/visita-anexo-masp/poste-fio.jpg" length="177724" type="image/jpeg"></enclosure><guid isPermaLink="false">galleries/visita-anexo-masp/poste-fio.jpg</guid><pubDate>Thu, 26 Jun 2025 10:17:29 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>